 />\n佢哋可能唔會明 <br />\n要做好啲文宣<br />\n<br />\n同埋 你要求人哋不割蓆<br />\n但人哋畀意思你又屌人左膠係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:33:58.000Z","msg":"*意見"},{"pid":"e4306f29d8d4aa7908b99981ceca2387569d5ee6","tid":1627572,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:36:31.000Z","msg":"同埋想講<br />\n如果藍嘅、中資嘅就爆<br />\n咁樣其實全香港七成嘅鋪頭都要爆<br />\n希望要爆嘅目標係有廣泛認可先爆<br />\n啲人係唔知你爆匯豐做咩㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e244b7c2ff5c1dfb3671630d4d203a5785df0c38","tid":1627572,"uid":46422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"Agree. Pushh"},{"pid":"9cff214f68a1002cbb63f60399ab0b2fbe02d2f4","tid":1627572,"uid":202889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"裝修(美心)文宣真係好多人睇，大家可以加推！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1626326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1626326</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zbSbQuh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzbSbQuh.jpg&h=aff8c5f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"639cf2335feb93dd3197222cf34059deaa339035","tid":1627572,"uid":32883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"裝修新手入一入黎 仲有召喚ust南亞仔同南亞手足<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1627570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1627570</a>"},{"pid":"766b9a93c7001abdd1d0bc2b6cf42b14c797cc38","tid":1627572,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4306f29d8d4aa7908b99981ceca2387569d5ee6","tid":1627572,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:36:31.000Z","msg":"同埋想講<br />\n如果藍嘅、中資嘅就爆<br />\n咁樣其實全香港七成嘅鋪頭都要爆<br />\n希望要爆嘅目標係有廣泛認可先爆<br />\n啲人係唔知你爆匯豐做咩㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"對準